MB（zip 较大） |\n| 空目录 | 4 个 | 0 |\n| web-search-mcp-server | 1 个目录 | ~几十 MB（venv 很大） |\n| temp_unzip | 1 个目录 | 未知 |\n| 其他 | 若干 | ~少量 |\n\n**大头是 `web-search-mcp-server/venv`**，Python 虚拟环境，估计有几十 MB。\n\n---\n\n头儿你看看想删哪些？我可以直接动手，或者你先确认一下。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":48595,"output":915,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49510,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772516240785}}
