{"type":"message","id":"e735882f","parentId":"30cd7ee8","timestamp":"2026-03-03T05:51:25.081Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_bcba5c10ad604471b8a5cbdb","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"ddgs_search\": {\n      \"command\": \"python\",\n      \"args\": [\"D:\\\\gooddog\\\\scripts\\\\mcp_ddgs_server.py\"]\n    },\n    \"dashscope_websearch\": {\n      \"url\": \"https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/api/v1/mcps/WebSearch/mcp\",\n      \"headers\": {\"Authorization\": \"Bearer sk-8937a309c5f04f909aabd1ad255b3654\"}\n    },\n    \"image-recognition\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@mcpcn/image-recognition-mcp\"],\n      \"env\": {\"DASHSCOPE_API_KEY\": \"sk-8937a309c5f04f909aabd1ad255b3654\"}\n    },\n    \"paddleocr-mcp\": {\n      \"command\": \"python\",\n      \"args\": [\"D:\\\\.openclaw\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\mcp-servers\\\\paddleocr-mcp\\\\server.py\"]\n    },\n    \"playwright\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@microsoft/playwright-mcp\"]\n    },\n    \"filesystem\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@modelcontextprotocol/server-filesystem\", \"D:\\\\.openclaw\"]\n    },\n    \"mcp-grep\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@247arjun/mcp-grep\"]\n    },\n    \"memory_search\": {\n      \"command\": \"python\",\n      \"args\": [\"D:\\\\memory-search-mcp\\\\mcp_memory_server.py\"],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"DASHSCOPE_API_KEY\": \"sk-8937a309c5f04f909aabd1ad255b3654\",\n        \"MEMORY_WORKSPACE\": \"D:\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\",\n        \"MEMORY_DB_PATH\": \"D:\\\\.openclaw\\\\memory\\\\search_index.sqlite\",\n        \"MEMORY_INCLUDE_SESSIONS\": \"1\"\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"imports\": []\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772517085078}}
{"type":"message","id":"6c331e86","parentId":"e735882f","timestamp":"2026-03-03T05:51:33.542Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看到了！`MEMORY_INCLUDE_SESSIONS=1` 说明应该包含 sessions，但可能 sessions 目录不在 workspace 下，或者需要指定 `MEMORY_SESSIONS_PATH`。\n\n让我看看 memory search 的源码，了解它怎么找 sessions 目录的。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a26bf7c60fe747d5b2cba1ba","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"D:\\memory-search-mcp\\mcp_memory_server.py","offset":1,"limit":100}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":55049,"output":173,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55222,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772517085081}}
{"type":"message","id":"cc1f7ebf","parentId":"6c331e86","timestamp":"2026-03-03T05:51:33.549Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a26bf7c60fe747d5b2cba1ba","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nMemory Search MCP Server\n记忆语义搜索 MCP 服务器（向量 + BM25 混合搜索），可对接 OpenClaw / mcporter 或任意 MCP 客户端。\n\n依赖: pip install -r requirements.txt\n运行: python mcp_memory_server.py   （stdio，由 mcporter 或 MCP 客户端启动）\n\n环境变量（必填）:\n  MEMORY_WORKSPACE   - 记忆文件根目录（内含 MEMORY.md、RECENT_MEMORY.md、memory/**/*.md）\n  MEMORY_DB_PATH     - SQLite 索引文件路径（如不指定则用 <MEMORY_WORKSPACE>/../.memory_search/search_index.sqlite）\n\nSession 扫描（可选）:\n  MEMORY_INCLUDE_SESSIONS - 设为 1 或 true 时，同时索引 agent session 对话（*.jsonl）\n  MEMORY_SESSIONS_DIR     - session 目录；不设时默认 <MEMORY_WORKSPACE>/../agents/main/sessions\n\nEmbedding（二选一）:\n  DASHSCOPE_API_KEY  - 阿里云 DashScope API Key（优先；未设时尝试从 ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json 的 env 中读取）\n  OPENAI_API_KEY     - OpenAI API Key（备选）\n  EMBEDDING_PROVIDER - 可选 \"dashscope\" | \"openai\"\n  EMBEDDING_MODEL    - 可选，默认 dashscope=text-embedding-v3, openai=text-embedding-3-small\n  EMBEDDING_BATCH_SIZE - 单次请求条数，默认 20（大文件如 MEMORY.md 会分批，避免超时/4xx）\n  EMBEDDING_TIMEOUT    - 单次请求超时秒数，默认 120\n\"\"\"\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport hashlib\nimport json\nimport os\nimport sqlite3\nimport sys\nimport time\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import List, Dict, Optional, Tuple\n\n# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 配置（均来自环境变量，无硬编码路径）\n# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\ndef _get_workspace_dir() -> Path:\n    v = os.environ.get(\"MEMORY_WORKSPACE\", \"\").strip()\n    if v:\n        return Path(v).resolve()\n    # 便携默认：脚本所在目录下的 workspace 文件夹\n    base = Path(__file__).resolve().parent\n    return base / \"workspace\"\n\n\ndef _get_db_path() -> Path:\n    v = os.environ.get(\"MEMORY_DB_PATH\", \"\").strip()\n    if v:\n        return Path(v).resolve()\n    # 便携默认：与 workspace 同级的 .memory_search/search_index.sqlite\n    ws = _get_workspace_dir()\n    return ws.parent / \".memory_search\" / \"search_index.sqlite\"\n\n\ndef _get_sessions_dir(workspace: Path) -> Optional[Path]:\n    \"\"\"若启用 session 扫描，返回 session 目录；否则返回 None。\"\"\"\n    if os.environ.get(\"MEMORY_INCLUDE_SESSIONS\", \"\").strip().lower() not in (\"1\", \"true\", \"yes\"):\n        return None\n    v = os.environ.get(\"MEMORY_SESSIONS_DIR\", \"\").strip()\n    if v:\n        p = Path(v).resolve()\n        return p if p.is_dir() else None\n    # 默认：workspace 上级的 agents/main/sessions\n    default = workspace.parent / \"agents\" / \"main\" / \"sessions\"\n    return default if default.is_dir() else None\n\n\nWORKSPACE_DIR = _get_workspace_dir()\nDB_PATH = _get_db_path()\n\nCHUNK_MAX_TOKENS = 400\nCHUNK_OVERLAP = 80\nVECTOR_WEIGHT = 0.7\nTEXT_WEIGHT = 0.3\nDEFAULT_MAX_RESULTS = 6\nDEFAULT_MIN_SCORE = 0.35\n# Embedding 单次请求条数（DashScope 上限 10，OpenAI 可更大）\nEMBEDDING_BATCH_SIZE = int(os.environ.get(\"EMBEDDING_BATCH_SIZE\", \"10\"))\n# Embedding 请求超时（秒），可适当调大避免 60s 不够\nEMBEDDING_TIMEOUT = float(os.environ.get(\"EMBEDDING_TIMEOUT\", \"120\"))\n\n# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# Embedding Provider\n# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n_embedding_client = None\n_embedding_model = None\n_embedding_dimensions = None\n\n\ndef _get_dashscope_key_from_openclaw() -> str:\n    \"\"\"从 OpenClaw 的 openclaw.json 中读取 DASHSCOPE_API_KEY，找到后注入到 os.environ。\"\"\"\n    # 明确指定路径时只读该文件\n    explicit = os.environ.get(\"OPENCLAW_JSON_PATH\", \"\").strip()\n    if explicit:\n        candidates = [Path(explicit)]\n    else:\n        candidates = []\n\n[513 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772517093546}}
{"type":"message","id":"2aafd3a8","parentId":"cc1f7ebf","timestamp":"2026-03-03T05:51:43.211Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看到了！session 目录默认是 `workspace.parent / \"agents\" / \"main\" / \"sessions\"`，也就是 `D:\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\sessions`。\n\n但我刚才 `dir` 那个目录只有 9 个 jsonl 文件。让我看看实际有多少 session 文件，以及为什么只索引了 25 个。\n\n25 个文件应该是：\n- MEMORY.md\n- RECENT_MEMORY.md\n- memory/ 目录下的文件（2026-03-02.md, 2026-03-03.md, episodic/*.md 等）\n- sessions/*.jsonl（9 个）\n\n加起来差不多 25 个。但用户说 session 不止这么点，可能是因为：\n1. sessions 目录里有更多文件但我没看到\n2. 或者有些文件没被索引\n\n让我再仔细看看 sessions 目录。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_aed1d5a27ada43a5a149fe08","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"dir \"D:\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\sessions\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":56225,"output":440,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56665,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772517093549}}
