{"type":"message","id":"8bc6adf7","parentId":"1ca448cd","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:01:18.437Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说成本90，碳酸锂今天跌了13%。这是关键信息——我之前查到的数据显示碳酸锂期货最近很强势（2月26日涨超11%，3月2日报17.3万/吨），但用户说今天跌了13%，说明今天碳酸锂期货也崩了。\n\n成本90，现在股价81.73，亏损约9.2%。如果是重仓，这个跌幅确实难受。\n\n我需要：\n1. 确认碳酸锂期货今天的实际跌幅\n2. 分析这个跌幅对中矿资源的影响\n3. 给出实际建议\n\n让我再搜一下碳酸锂期货今天的行情。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6351bc35a43245f88d15f28a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"npx mcporter call dashscope_websearch.bailian_web_search query=\"碳酸锂期货 今天 跌幅 2026年3月3日 LC主力合约\" count=8"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":74601,"output":351,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74952,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772517628340}}
