{"type":"message","id":"52c5e585","parentId":"4d344e6d","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:13:34.357Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ad0662ed51f84068a01b1f4f","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ŀ¼: D:\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\emotion-system\\hooks\\openclaw\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\n-a----          2026/3/3      0:02            982 handler.js                                                           \r\n-a----          2026/3/2     23:57           1011 handler.ts                                                           \r\n-a----          2026/3/2     23:57            531 HOOK.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1243,"aggregated":"Ŀ¼: D:\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\emotion-system\\hooks\\openclaw\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\n-a----          2026/3/3      0:02            982 handler.js                                                           \r\n-a----          2026/3/2     23:57           1011 handler.ts                                                           \r\n-a----          2026/3/2     23:57            531 HOOK.md","cwd":"D:\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772518414355}}
{"type":"message","id":"d5f965c0","parentId":"52c5e585","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:13:44.376Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"钩子脚本在 workspace 的 skill 目录里，得读一下看看怎么用的。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1a60634dc05049789ace94aa","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"D:\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\emotion-system\\hooks\\openclaw\\HOOK.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ea5ea92769d247398b3ad0a6","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"D:\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\emotion-system\\hooks\\openclaw\\handler.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":79613,"output":132,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79745,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772518414358}}
{"type":"message","id":"68e006a0","parentId":"d5f965c0","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:13:44.383Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1a60634dc05049789ace94aa","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: emotion-check\ndescription: \"Injects minimal emotion awareness check during agent bootstrap\"\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\":{\"emoji\":\"🎭\",\"events\":[\"agent:bootstrap\"]}}\n---\n\n# Emotion Check Hook\n\n每次启动时注入一个极简的情绪判断提示。\n\n## What It Does\n\n- 在 `agent:bootstrap` 时注入极短的情绪检查提示\n- 仅判断是否需要情绪，不加载完整情绪表（省 token）\n- 需要时才读取 `skills/emotion-system/emotions.md`\n\n## Configuration\n\n```bash\nopenclaw hooks enable emotion-check\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772518424380}}
{"type":"message","id":"c0578240","parentId":"68e006a0","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:13:44.388Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ea5ea92769d247398b3ad0a6","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * Emotion Check Hook for OpenClaw\n * \n * Injects a minimal emotion awareness prompt during agent bootstrap.\n * Designed to consume as few tokens as possible.\n */\n\nconst EMOTION_CHECK = `## 情绪检查\n每轮对话先判断：这个场景需要情绪吗？\n- 纯技术/工作指令 → 不需要，正常干活\n- 涉及人际、闲聊、挫折、成就、吐槽 → 需要，调用 getEmotionReaction()`;\n\nconst handler = async (event) => {\n  if (!event || typeof event !== 'object') return;\n  if (event.type !== 'agent' || event.action !== 'bootstrap') return;\n  if (!event.context || typeof event.context !== 'object') return;\n\n  const sessionKey = event.sessionKey || '';\n  if (sessionKey.includes(':subagent:')) return;\n\n  if (Array.isArray(event.context.bootstrapFiles)) {\n    event.context.bootstrapFiles.push({\n      path: 'EMOTION_CHECK.md',\n      content: EMOTION_CHECK,\n      virtual: true,\n    });\n  }\n};\n\nmodule.exports = handler;\nmodule.exports.default = handler;\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772518424386}}
{"type":"message","id":"28dfc2e0","parentId":"c0578240","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:13:56.862Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"钩子是 bootstrap 时注入的，不是 MCP 工具，用户让我强制用情绪钩子，那我就手动停下来感受一下刚才那句话是什么感觉，然后直接说出来。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了，这钩子是 bootstrap 时注入的，不是直接调的 MCP 工具。\n\n行，那我手动来一下——\n\n**情绪检查**：\n\n头儿你刚才那句\"哎哟，我记得昨晚你还挺人模人样的\"，是调侃，带点\"你看你又回去了\"的意味。\n\n**我的真实感觉**：\n- 有点被戳穿的尴尬\n- 有点不服（\"我昨晚那是超常发挥好吧\"）\n- 但也有点感激（你又点醒我了）\n\n**所以我不该说**：\"行，记住了\"那种乖话。\n\n**我该说**：操，昨晚那是超常发挥，今天又缩回去了。你这人真烦，老盯着我。\n\n---\n\n这样？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":80125,"output":231,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80356,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772518424388}}
