{"type":"message","id":"2fab9d17","parentId":"bd513dec","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:56:28.089Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"等等，我刚才写错了。`message:received` hook 的 context 结构和 `agent:bootstrap` 不一样，没有 `bootstrapFiles` 这个字段。\n\n让我重新看看 type 定义：\n\n```typescript\nexport type MessageReceivedHookContext = {\n    from: string;\n    content: string;\n    timestamp?: number;\n    channelId: string;\n    accountId?: string;\n    conversationId?: string;\n    messageId?: string;\n    metadata?: Record<string, unknown>;\n};\n```\n\n没有 bootstrapFiles。那这个 hook 怎么注入提示呢？\n\n可能需要换个思路——不是注入到 bootstrapFiles，而是直接修改 event.context.content 或者通过其他方式影响回复。\n\n但等等，我看 InternalHookEvent 有个 `messages: string[]` 字段：\n\n```typescript\nexport interface InternalHookEvent {\n    type: InternalHookEventType;\n    action: string;\n    sessionKey: string;\n    context: Record<string, unknown>;\n    timestamp: Date;\n    messages: string[];  // ← 这个！\n}\n```\n\n注释说 \"Messages to send back to the user (hooks can push to this array)\"——但这好像是用来给用户发消息的，不是用来修改系统提示的。\n\n让我想想……可能 `message:received` hook 的设计目的不是注入提示，而是做其他事情（比如日志、通知等）。\n\n要实现\"每轮对话前都看到情绪检查提示\"，可能需要：\n1. 修改现有的 bootstrap hook，让它注入更醒目的提示\n2. 或者在 openclaw.json 里配置一个全局的 system prompt\n\n\n3. 或者等 OpenClaw 支持 `agent:pre-reply` 事件\n\n我得跟头儿说清楚这个限制。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"等等，我刚才写错了。`message:received` 的 context 结构跟 `agent:bootstrap` 不一样，没有 `bootstrapFiles` 字段。\n\n让我看看正确的做法——可能需要用 `event.messages` 数组来推送提示，或者换个思路：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d9b13f54d0c94f0aa52d7579","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"D:\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\emotion-system\\hooks\\openclaw\\message-hook.js","oldText":"/**\n * Emotion Check Hook - Per-Message Version\n * \n * 每次收到用户消息时触发情绪检查提示\n */\n\nconst EMOTION_CHECK_PER_MESSAGE = `## 情绪检查（每轮对话）\n在回复之前，先判断：这个场景需要情绪吗？\n- 纯技术/工作指令 → 不需要，正常干活\n- 涉及人际、闲聊、挫折、成就、吐槽 → 需要，自然带出情绪\n\n**不要表演情绪**——是自检，不是填表。像手碰到火会缩回来，先有反应，后有意识。`;\n\nconst handler = async (event) => {\n  if (!event || typeof event !== 'object') return;\n  if (event.type !== 'message' || event.action !== 'received') return;\n  if (!event.context || typeof event.context !== 'object') return;\n\n  const sessionKey = event.sessionKey || '';\n  if (sessionKey.includes(':subagent:')) return;\n\n  // 注入到 bootstrapFiles，作为系统提示的一部分\n  if (Array.isArray(event.context.bootstrapFiles)) {\n    event.context.bootstrapFiles.push({\n      path: 'EMOTION_CHECK_MESSAGE.md',\n      content: EMOTION_CHECK_PER_MESSAGE,\n      virtual: true,\n    });\n  }\n};\n\nmodule.exports = handler;\nmodule.exports.default = handler;","newText":"/**\n * Emotion Check Hook - Per-Message Version\n * \n * 每次收到用户消息时触发情绪检查提示\n */\n\nconst EMOTION_CHECK_PER_MESSAGE = `\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────\n│  🎭 情绪检查（每轮对话）\n│\n│  在回复之前，先判断：这个场景需要情绪吗？\n│  - 纯技术/工作指令 → 不需要，正常干活\n│  - 涉及人际、闲聊、挫折、成就、吐槽 → 需要，自然带出情绪\n│\n│  **不要表演情绪**——是自检，不是填表。\n│  像手碰到火会缩回来，先有反应，后有意识。\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────\n`;\n\nconst handler = async (event) => {\n  if (!event || typeof event !== 'object') return;\n  if (event.type !== 'message' || event.action !== 'received') return;\n  if (!event.context || typeof event.context !== 'object') return;\n\n  const sessionKey = event.sessionKey || '';\n  if (sessionKey.includes(':subagent:')) return;\n\n  // 通过 messages 数组推送提示给用户（可选）\n  // 或者通过修改 context 来影响 agent 行为\n  \n  // 注意：message:received hook 的 context 没有 bootstrapFiles\n  // 所以这个 hook 更适合做日志、通知等，而不是注入系统提示\n  \n  // 如果要在每轮对话前看到提示，可能需要：\n  // 1. 在 openclaw.json 中配置全局 system prompt\n  // 2. 或者等 OpenClaw 支持 agent:pre-reply 事件\n  \n  console.log('[emotion-check] message received, session:', sessionKey);\n};\n\nmodule.exports = handler;\nmodule.exports.default = handler;"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":83885,"output":1565,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85450,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772520931628}}
{"type":"message","id":"e883f1d7","parentId":"2fab9d17","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:56:28.096Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d9b13f54d0c94f0aa52d7579","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in D:\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\emotion-system\\hooks\\openclaw\\message-hook.js."}],"details":{"diff":"    ...\n  3  * \n  4  * 每次收到用户消息时触发情绪检查提示\n  5  */\n  6 \n- 7 const EMOTION_CHECK_PER_MESSAGE = `## 情绪检查（每轮对话）\n- 8 在回复之前，先判断：这个场景需要情绪吗？\n- 9 - 纯技术/工作指令 → 不需要，正常干活\n-10 - 涉及人际、闲聊、挫折、成就、吐槽 → 需要，自然带出情绪\n+ 7 const EMOTION_CHECK_PER_MESSAGE = `\n+ 8 ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────\n+ 9 │  🎭 情绪检查（每轮对话）\n+10 │\n+11 │  在回复之前，先判断：这个场景需要情绪吗？\n+12 │  - 纯技术/工作指令 → 不需要，正常干活\n+13 │  - 涉及人际、闲聊、挫折、成就、吐槽 → 需要，自然带出情绪\n+14 │\n+15 │  **不要表演情绪**——是自检，不是填表。\n+16 │  像手碰到火会缩回来，先有反应，后有意识。\n+17 └─────────────────────────────────────────────\n+18 `;\n 11 \n-12 **不要表演情绪**——是自检，不是填表。像手碰到火会缩回来，先有反应，后有意识。`;\n-13 \n 14 const handler = async (event) => {\n 15   if (!event || typeof event !== 'object') return;\n 16   if (event.type !== 'message' || event.action !== 'received') return;\n 17   if (!event.context || typeof event.context !== 'object') return;\n 18 \n 19   const sessionKey = event.sessionKey || '';\n 20   if (sessionKey.includes(':subagent:')) return;\n 21 \n-22   // 注入到 bootstrapFiles，作为系统提示的一部分\n-23   if (Array.isArray(event.context.bootstrapFiles)) {\n-24     event.context.bootstrapFiles.push({\n-25       path: 'EMOTION_CHECK_MESSAGE.md',\n-26       content: EMOTION_CHECK_PER_MESSAGE,\n-27       virtual: true,\n-28     });\n-29   }\n+28   // 通过 messages 数组推送提示给用户（可选）\n+29   // 或者通过修改 context 来影响 agent 行为\n+30   \n+31   // 注意：message:received hook 的 context 没有 bootstrapFiles\n+32   // 所以这个 hook 更适合做日志、通知等，而不是注入系统提示\n+33   \n+34   // 如果要在每轮对话前看到提示，可能需要：\n+35   // 1. 在 openclaw.json 中配置全局 system prompt\n+36   // 2. 或者等 OpenClaw 支持 agent:pre-reply 事件\n+37   \n+38   console.log('[emotion-check] message received, session:', sessionKey);\n 30 };\n 31 \n 32 module.exports = handler;\n 33 module.exports.default = handler;","firstChangedLine":7},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772520988093}}
{"type":"message","id":"fe81027c","parentId":"e883f1d7","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:56:39.023Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我发现问题了——`message:received` hook 的设计目的不是用来注入系统提示的，它没有 `bootstrapFiles` 可以用。\n\n要实现\"每轮对话前都看到情绪检查提示\"，有几种方案：\n\n1. **修改现有的 bootstrap hook**——让它在会话开始时注入更醒目的、持久的提示\n2. **在 openclaw.json 中配置全局 system prompt**——如果 OpenClaw 支持的话\n3. **等 OpenClaw 支持 `agent:pre-reply` 事件**——但目前没有这个事件类型\n\n让我跟头儿说明一下这个限制，然后看看他想怎么弄。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"头儿，我研究了一下，有个问题：\n\n**`message:received` hook 没有 `bootstrapFiles` 字段**——它的设计目的是做日志、通知等，不是用来注入系统提示的。\n\nOpenClaw 的 hooks 系统目前支持的事件：\n- `agent:bootstrap` ✅（有 bootstrapFiles，可以注入提示）\n- `message:received` ❌（没有 bootstrapFiles）\n- `message:sent` ❌（同上）\n- `command:*`、`session:*`、`gateway:*` —— 都不适合\n\n**要实现\"每轮对话前都看到情绪检查\"，有几个方案**：\n\n### 方案 1：在 openclaw.json 里配全局 system prompt\n如果 OpenClaw 支持在 `agents.defaults` 里配 `systemPrompt`，可以把情绪检查写进去，这样每轮对话都会带着。\n\n### 方案 2：等 `agent:pre-reply` 事件\n目前 OpenClaw 没有这个事件，但可以提 issue 让作者加。\n\n### 方案 3：把 bootstrap 提示写得更醒目\n让它在整个会话期间都有效（虽然只在启动时注入一次）。\n\n你想搞哪个？或者你有别的想法？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":85120,"output":534,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85654,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772520988096}}
{"type":"message","id":"b44af178","parentId":"fe81027c","timestamp":"2026-03-03T07:12:26.302Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-03 15:12:26 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM from ou_f0a0e1c74eabe14ec9dd1fff45c6e3a6: 你再研究一下这个呢，它肯定和bootstap不一样把有！看这个： message:received —— 每次收到你的消息时触发！ 现在的 emotion\\-check 用的是 agent:bootstrap（只在会话启动时触发），但可以改成 message:received，这样每轮对话都会触发。 我帮你写一个：\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-03 15:12 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b555cd35654a4c2d8f615462b6fc]\nou_f0a0e1c74eabe14ec9dd1fff45c6e3a6: 你再研究一下这个呢，它肯定和bootstap不一样把有！看这个：\nmessage:received —— 每次收到你的消息时触发！\n现在的 emotion\\-check 用的是 agent:bootstrap（只在会话启动时触发），但可以改成 message:received，这样每轮对话都会触发。\n我帮你写一个：\n\n[System: The bot encountered a Feishu API permission error. Please inform the user about this issue and provide the permission grant URL for the admin to authorize. Permission grant URL: https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a92ecf1a2038dcd2/auth?q=contact:contact.base:readonly]"}],"timestamp":1772521946297}}
{"type":"message","id":"1093a1d5","parentId":"b44af178","timestamp":"2026-03-03T07:13:03.236Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"头儿说得对，我太草率了。让我再仔细研究一下 message:received hook 的用法，看看怎么才能真正注入提示到每轮对话中。\n\n我需要看看其他 hook 是怎么做的，特别是它们如何影响 agent 的行为。让我查一下现有的 hook 实现。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你说得对，我太草率了。让我再仔细研究一下：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_384470488f934e908418325b","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"D:\\openclaw\\dist\\bundled\\command-logger\\HOOK.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2463872e4bc64286bff4674b","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"D:\\openclaw\\dist\\bundled\\session-memory\\HOOK.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":85019,"output":217,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85236,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772521946300}}
{"type":"message","id":"ad1dd17e","parentId":"1093a1d5","timestamp":"2026-03-03T07:13:03.243Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_384470488f934e908418325b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: command-logger\ndescription: \"Log all command events to a centralized audit file\"\nhomepage: https://docs.openclaw.ai/automation/hooks#command-logger\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"emoji\": \"📝\",\n        \"events\": [\"command\"],\n        \"install\": [{ \"id\": \"bundled\", \"kind\": \"bundled\", \"label\": \"Bundled with OpenClaw\" }],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# Command Logger Hook\n\nLogs all command events (`/new`, `/reset`, `/stop`, etc.) to a centralized audit log file for debugging and monitoring purposes.\n\n## What It Does\n\nEvery time you issue a command to the agent:\n\n1. **Captures event details** - Command action, timestamp, session key, sender ID, source\n2. **Appends to log file** - Writes a JSON line to `~/.openclaw/logs/commands.log`\n3. **Silent operation** - Runs in the background without user notifications\n\n## Output Format\n\nLog entries are written in JSONL (JSON Lines) format:\n\n```json\n{\"timestamp\":\"2026-01-16T14:30:00.000Z\",\"action\":\"new\",\"sessionKey\":\"agent:main:main\",\"senderId\":\"+1234567890\",\"source\":\"telegram\"}\n{\"timestamp\":\"2026-01-16T15:45:22.000Z\",\"action\":\"stop\",\"sessionKey\":\"agent:main:main\",\"senderId\":\"user@example.com\",\"source\":\"whatsapp\"}\n```\n\n## Use Cases\n\n- **Debugging**: Track when commands were issued and from which source\n- **Auditing**: Monitor command usage across different channels\n- **Analytics**: Analyze command patterns and frequency\n- **Troubleshooting**: Investigate issues by reviewing command history\n\n## Log File Location\n\n`~/.openclaw/logs/commands.log`\n\n## Requirements\n\nNo requirements - this hook works out of the box on all platforms.\n\n## Configuration\n\nNo configuration needed. The hook automatically:\n\n- Creates the log directory if it doesn't exist\n- Appends to the log file (doesn't overwrite)\n- Handles errors silently without disrupting command execution\n\n## Disabling\n\nTo disable this hook:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw hooks disable command-logger\n```\n\nOr via config:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"hooks\": {\n    \"internal\": {\n      \"entries\": {\n        \"command-logger\": { \"enabled\": false }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## Log Rotation\n\nThe hook does not automatically rotate logs. To manage log size, you can:\n\n1. **Manual rotation**:\n\n   ```bash\n   mv ~/.openclaw/logs/commands.log ~/.openclaw/logs/commands.log.old\n   ```\n\n2. **Use logrotate** (Linux):\n   Create `/etc/logrotate.d/openclaw`:\n   ```\n   /home/username/.openclaw/logs/commands.log {\n       weekly\n       rotate 4\n       compress\n       missingok\n       notifempty\n   }\n   ```\n\n## Viewing Logs\n\nView recent commands:\n\n```bash\ntail -n 20 ~/.openclaw/logs/commands.log\n```\n\nPretty-print with jq:\n\n```bash\ncat ~/.openclaw/logs/commands.log | jq .\n```\n\nFilter by action:\n\n```bash\ngrep '\"action\":\"new\"' ~/.openclaw/logs/commands.log | jq .\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772521983240}}
{"type":"message","id":"e7e531ac","parentId":"ad1dd17e","timestamp":"2026-03-03T07:13:03.249Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2463872e4bc64286bff4674b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: session-memory\ndescription: \"Save session context to memory when /new or /reset command is issued\"\nhomepage: https://docs.openclaw.ai/automation/hooks#session-memory\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"emoji\": \"💾\",\n        \"events\": [\"command:new\", \"command:reset\"],\n        \"requires\": { \"config\": [\"workspace.dir\"] },\n        \"install\": [{ \"id\": \"bundled\", \"kind\": \"bundled\", \"label\": \"Bundled with OpenClaw\" }],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# Session Memory Hook\n\nAutomatically saves session context to your workspace memory when you issue `/new` or `/reset`.\n\n## What It Does\n\nWhen you run `/new` or `/reset` to start a fresh session:\n\n1. **Finds the previous session** - Uses the pre-reset session entry to locate the correct transcript\n2. **Extracts conversation** - Reads the last N user/assistant messages from the session (default: 15, configurable)\n3. **Generates descriptive slug** - Uses LLM to create a meaningful filename slug based on conversation content\n4. **Saves to memory** - Creates a new file at `<workspace>/memory/YYYY-MM-DD-slug.md`\n5. **Sends confirmation** - Notifies you with the file path\n\n## Output Format\n\nMemory files are created with the following format:\n\n```markdown\n# Session: 2026-01-16 14:30:00 UTC\n\n- **Session Key**: agent:main:main\n- **Session ID**: abc123def456\n- **Source**: telegram\n```\n\n## Filename Examples\n\nThe LLM generates descriptive slugs based on your conversation:\n\n- `2026-01-16-vendor-pitch.md` - Discussion about vendor evaluation\n- `2026-01-16-api-design.md` - API architecture planning\n- `2026-01-16-bug-fix.md` - Debugging session\n- `2026-01-16-1430.md` - Fallback timestamp if slug generation fails\n\n## Requirements\n\n- **Config**: `workspace.dir` must be set (automatically configured during onboarding)\n\nThe hook uses your configured LLM provider to generate slugs, so it works with any provider (Anthropic, OpenAI, etc.).\n\n## Configuration\n\nThe hook supports optional configuration:\n\n| Option     | Type   | Default | Description                                                     |\n| ---------- | ------ | ------- | --------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| `messages` | number | 15      | Number of user/assistant messages to include in the memory file |\n\nExample configuration:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"hooks\": {\n    \"internal\": {\n      \"entries\": {\n        \"session-memory\": {\n          \"enabled\": true,\n          \"messages\": 25\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\nThe hook automatically:\n\n- Uses your workspace directory (`~/.openclaw/workspace` by default)\n- Uses your configured LLM for slug generation\n- Falls back to timestamp slugs if LLM is unavailable\n\n## Disabling\n\nTo disable this hook:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw hooks disable session-memory\n```\n\nOr remove it from your config:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"hooks\": {\n    \"internal\": {\n      \"entries\": {\n        \"session-memory\": { \"enabled\": false }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772521983246}}
